Text-Xtangle version 0.006

This module provides you to generate a template perl source code
from a given XHTML and a presentation logic script as like as
the Kwartz-Ruby template system.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install

DEPENDENCIES

Encode

